Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:19.06,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Oowarai Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:37.85,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:41.04,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Tou~ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:51.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I am away from Academy City, spending time at the beach with Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:54.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, this wasn't voluntary on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:56.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of this city right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.07,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the higher-ups are getting cranky about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:04.15,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate... Kamijyo-chan,\Nyou'll be in a dangerous situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:06.15,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,so until the dust settles...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:08.57,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,...is what a couple of higher-ups are thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:13.23,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and the place you'll be going to is... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:14.87,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.97,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:18.43,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:20.71,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:23.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the first time I go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,"No" means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:30.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're an illegal alien who doesn't even have a valid ID!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:34.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you try to tag along,\NI bet you'll get stopped at the city limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:40.07,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:46.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world did he just let us go without a second look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...but yeah, just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:52.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,we ended up here for some odd reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:58.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And I just get a bad feeling from the name of the place they chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:58.66,Note,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Oowarai" means big laugh/joke/jeer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.18,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Tou~ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:04.77,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I found a cute hat, and I'm going to give it to you as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.39,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.47,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.00,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Beware - Large Jellyfish Outbreak - Oowarai Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:15.17,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}Quite a misfortune you experienced so soon after your arrival...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:16.80,Title,woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(1158,523)}#15 Angel Fall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:18.99,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,This year's jellyfish season came quite early though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.45,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to that, we have no guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.13,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:28.30,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It was really the first time I've seen a jellyfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.50,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.60,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I will come back to retrieve the first-aid kit later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:33.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, th-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.93,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:41.35,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,We just got a call from your party-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.80,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,-that they'd be arriving late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.91,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,That they'll arrive tomorrow morning-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.47,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought we were going to see them soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:51.71,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma's-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:51.71,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.00,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.57,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.14,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.86,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.60,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was supposed to meet them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:13.17,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo Touya and Kamijyo Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My parents, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.82,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:29.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't see them that often, Komoe-sensei seems to be taking care of me more than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems a cousin I grew up with is coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:38.28,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.67,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of people are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What kind? Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:48.22,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to seeing your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.65,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:53.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out tomorrow, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.17,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You're being a meanie again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.11,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,How much could it hurt to tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:05.81,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And you're always, always so cold, so cruel, so blunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.09,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,so rude, so brusque, so indifferent,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:11.25,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,so unregretful, so hard to grasp-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.86,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll find out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:18.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my memories, so I obviously don't remember how my parents are,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:24.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of people they were, or what kind of son I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to act naturally before them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:33.62,Default,Shiz,0000,0000,0000,,The red-hot Hitotsui Hajime-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.46,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:44.35,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,As such, I'm uncharacteristically nervous right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, will they find out I lost my memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no point worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:56.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The fun will start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.90,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.40,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,Your party just called now-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.58,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,-that they will arrive soon-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:57.85,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.78,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.83,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Anything different?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:11.60,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I wanted to hand you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.19,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I went to India on my last business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:19.11,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,This is a souvenir, a local deity called something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.33,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.86,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if you're meeting me for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.20,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, let me get your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.48,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Take Mom's and Otohime-chan's, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.72,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.84,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This person is my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.59,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about our arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.27,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to get here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:50.65,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we just moved,\Nso we don't know where things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Move?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.07,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.61,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,We went over this on the phone last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:55.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever be able to see the home I was born in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.92,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.42,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.30,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's my cousin-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.71,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.12,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:25.19,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, Oniichan! I wanted to see you so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.92,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma-oniichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.43,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea later! The sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.49,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.56,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What, Oniichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Not "what"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And what's with your disgusting sister acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.29,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister or Sister-in-Law - That is the issue, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:44.29,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring someone like her here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, since when did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.14,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "someone like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.44,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "since when did I know her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.64,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,She's your cousin, Otohime-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, yo, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:00.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My back-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.08,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,They're touching my back-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.94,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:09.51,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx99}Touma-san, is being hugged by Otohime-chan embarrassing because you haven't experienced it in some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.02,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.75,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san, is-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.92,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you sleeping like a pig in the room just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:21.84,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Changing your clothing and teleporting, who are you, Shirai Kuroko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:26.04,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And! What's with your obvious madam-like, señora-like way of speech?! {tilda over the n, if possible}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.05,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.12,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.19,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Talking like that to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:36.70,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I said, what's with you talking that rudely to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that this girl, who looks like she'd get kicked out of a R-15 movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...is my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.82,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.73,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san, are you saying your mom appears younger than her age?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And that this electrifying shocker of a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...is my cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.22,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:09.08,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,They are your mother and Otohime-chan, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.34,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:22.81,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? EVERYTHING!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is this surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the "You've been punked" sign?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Playing around with the tender soul of a young man like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:34.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of grudge do you guys have against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.80,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, calm down, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.41,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.89,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,The swimsuit girl drawn on this pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.83,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Flip it and-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.30,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.01,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going in the middle of our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.86,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Oniichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:48.92,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Toying with me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.22,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought my dad would be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.15,Default,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.93,Default,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,We have been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.99,Default,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,Please... come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.91,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:04.91,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're part of this, too, Misaka sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Since when were you hiding here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.38,Default,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.05,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, please don't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.68,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bit emotional since we haven't seen each other in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.40,Default,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for staying here at our resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.62,Default,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I will take you to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.40,Default,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:35.38,Default,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your friend is awake now it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.18,Default,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.18,Default,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat breakfast already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:49.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,AHHHHHHHHHHHHH---
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.73,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.78,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am at the beach with a Misaka Mikoto that's wearing a school swimsuit and pretending to be a sister character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:22.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, this wasn't voluntary on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to play a part in this, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.91,Default-alt,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.39,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, calm down, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:34.85,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,In times like these, just take a dip and cool your head, Oniichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.21,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come over afterwards, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:47.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But how long is this comedy act going to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:49.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's no longer at the level of\N"You've been punked!" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.97,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Cooled your head a bit now, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.14,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're worrying about, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.90,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.34,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a souvenir I got on my business trip to Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:01.54,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:02.94,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:03.49,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.73,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.58,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.85,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san, Dad's taste doesn't work on you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You... that-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.30,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.24,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,That looks perfect on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.44,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It was a great idea for me to have gotten you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:25.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who bought this swimsuit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your taste, as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:27.75,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.65,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,If you go around the world on business trips,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.66,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,you start to see that Japanese women need to be refined a bit-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.73,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to me so suddenly, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that my father is a failure of a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that he is just a damn lolicon pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.68,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.27,Default,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.10,Default,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Tou~ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.09,Default,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.65,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Oniichan, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.81,Default,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:02.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.70,Default,tv,0000,0000,0000,,Next in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.10,Default,tv,0000,0000,0000,,With the political scandal that has shaken up the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:15.14,Default,tv,0000,0000,0000,,the President will be holding a press conference to explain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.43,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's the doc doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.18,Default,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Komori reporting from Washington, D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.61,Default,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,With the suspicions surrounding the Office this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.25,Default,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,it will be interesting to see what stance the President takes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.62,Default,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,and what will be said-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.49,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.70,Default-alt,!Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can't see, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.26,Default,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,The President has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.04,Default,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,She is showing a calm, nonchalant face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.66,Default,!Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.39,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is Shirai Kuroko doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.63,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is way too ridiculous no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.81,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is too well planned for a surprise trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's no point in crossing the ocean just to do this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming it's not a prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.88,Default,men,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.10,Default,men,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.39,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take this hill road in front of you and go straight-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.89,Default,oldota,0000,0000,0000,,Shana-tan, moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.86,Default,oldho,0000,0000,0000,,This person's uber annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.54,Default,...,0000,0000,0000,,Drop the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.56,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Oniichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.11,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.99,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,This was a photo from New Year's last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.72,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me now, Touma-oniichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.42,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.84,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,You're really weird today, Oniichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The girl in this picture is my cousin-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.14,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.00,Default,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsugami Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:31.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She can't tell that her own appearance is different in this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if everyone's inside and outside are "inside out".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:41.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And they don't realize it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo Touma knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,He knows from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not in my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:04.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,he knows that people that show up in these crazy cosplays are usually his acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, in these situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,the attitude I should take is-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, long time no-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.18,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,-see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.80,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Question no. 1 - Are you the spellcaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:15.18,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Asking question no. 1 again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:16.97,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the spellcaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.31,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.54,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It is rash to say that this young man is the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.87,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, glad we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:32.61,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,And he actually sees me properly as Tsuchimikado Motoharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.42,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:37.42,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that he can properly recognize you must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.75,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:41.76,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see any traces of that on Kami-yan's body at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:45.57,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We must consider him the same as us; that he was able to escape the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.72,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magician from the English Purist Church, Necessarius,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.76,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.00,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I came here for the same reason as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.06,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,To determine the origin of this distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:59.17,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is unreasonable to conclude that this young man is the caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.71,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magician from the Russian Orthodox Church, Annihilatus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:06.73,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Misha Kreuzhev. {anyone know russian names?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:12.31,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, to be able to see a magician of Annihilatus here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.87,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Question no. 1 - What evidence do you have to say that this man isn't the caster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:19.22,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Question no. 2 - If not this man, who is the caster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:22.08,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I can't tell what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, what is Tsuchimikado doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:28.13,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,This young man is not a magician, but an esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.59,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,And his level is-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys just going to ignore the fact that I was almost killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just gonna ignore me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:35.96,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,How disagreeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.00,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Your rudeness and vulgar attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.02,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you haven't grown at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This person is my acquaintance, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I played dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:50.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,At least tell me what's going on here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Kanzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.74,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.60,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to let all concerned members know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.07,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,else we cannot move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.55,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Concerned member?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.79,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, a certain magic spell is spreading around the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.16,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The structure and formula of the magic is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:12.82,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,For convenience purposes, we are calling this magic "Angel Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.26,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of the Tree of Sephiroth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:21.46,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I say it's a graph that ranks the spiritual classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.76,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Supreme One, angels, and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.68,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, there is no way a human can attain the rank of an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.75,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,And the other way around certainly is impossible, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:33.21,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, all classes are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.75,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,However, when an angel falls to the human class-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:37.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Time out for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.18,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Having a hard time understanding, as expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:46.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but... angels? This is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:50.89,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You should've experienced, firsthand, the effects of this spell, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:51.55,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Effects?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.80,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the switching of appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.68,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The emergence of this messed up world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.88,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,From the distortion caused by the fall of an angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:03.63,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,the "appearance" and "content" of\Nthe human world has been completely messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:06.49,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the musical chair game is all about first come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:09.47,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,"Appearance" will quickly take the place of "content".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.16,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,As a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the fact that everyone's appearance is being switched around is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:17.82,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,While we don't know by whom and\Nfor what purpose this magic was cast,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:21.19,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,the important thing is the person in the middle of this distortion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:23.23,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...and that is you, Kami-yan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:27.59,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You are the number one suspect in the Angel Fall incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.12,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You escaped the effects of the magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:32.42,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,and from the viewpoint of the magicians who are trying to stop the effects from spreading,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.39,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,you are one who will be targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:39.15,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, it is hard to reason\Nthe true suspect is Kamijyo Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:42.20,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,One, he does not possess any magical knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:48.98,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Two, we cannot see any trace of the "load"\Ntypically seen on espers who have used magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.65,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Rebuttal no. 1 - This man has not been affected by the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:19:00.75,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, he's got the Imagine Breaker that can nullify any kind of illusion in this world with his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:01.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:07.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado, how do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.06,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Number value: 40, 9, 30, 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.51,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Sum of 86.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:18.06,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Corresponding to "O' water,\Nbecome a serpent and strike like a sword"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.87,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:29.56,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,I acknowledge this explanation as evidence for clearing him from suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:34.38,Default,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, I apologize here for pointing\Nmy blade at you for the wrong reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.47,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.75,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you no longer have any suspicion on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:42.54,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,it is a fact that Angel Fall is centered around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.28,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,There is a high probability that the caster is near Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:49.62,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It is hard to imagine that a single caster is responsible for a spell of this scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:53.79,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a ritual location that has a barrier or a magical seal deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.58,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,We'd need to destroy the ritual location...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.91,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...or defeat the caster himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:01.09,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two ways to stop an Angel Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.55,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, Tsuchimikado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you on this side of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about my right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.17,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.21,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a member of Necessarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.97,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.93,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for the caster that started Angel Fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado and I headed for Dad's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The horrible finding we made there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Kamijyo Touya".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
